Hey everyone, few hours left, if you have not voted, please do vote for us in Gitcoin Grants Privacy Round.

We are building BeYou, a privacy preserving anonymous social platform that enables anonymous communication, feedback, and voting within verified communities.

It would be really helpful if you could vote for us in the Gitcoin Grants Privacy round. It takes no money but only 2 minutes to vote.
